descp2: An optional list of `ints`. Defaults to `[1, 1, 1, 1]`. 1-D tensor of length 4.  The dilation factor for each dimension of`input`. If set to k > 1, there will be k-1 skipped cells between each filter element on that dimension. The dimension order is determined by the value of`data_format`, see above for details. Dilations in the batch and depth dimensions must be 1.
